description:
Creates a Payload CMS 3.0 NumberField configuration

Example:
```typescript
{
  name: 'price',
  type: 'number',
  required: true,
  label: 'Product Price',
  min: 0,
  max: 1000,
  // Custom validation example
  validate: (value) => {
    if (value && value % 1 !== 0) {
      return 'Price must be a whole number';
    }
    return true;
  }
}
```

template:
{
  name: '{name}', // Database field name
  type: 'number',
  label: 'Number Field', // Label shown in the admin UI
  required: true,
  min: 0,
  max: 1000,
  // Optional: Add custom validation
  validate: (value) => {
    if (value && value % 1 !== 0) {
      return 'Please enter a whole number';
    }
    return true; // Return true if valid
  },
}
